OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F391A1778483138
OL,3,CRochdale secures promotion with
OL,4,Cpenalty shootout win
OL,6,FRochdale produced a dramatic late
OL,7,Ffightback from 2-0 down to clinch
OL,8,Fpromotion back to the EFL with a
OL,9,Fpenalty shoot-out victory over Boreham
OL,10,FWood.
OL,12,FThe Wood looked set for glory in the
OL,13,FEnterprise National League play-off
OL,14,Ffinal at Wembley after striking in
OL,15,Feach half through Matt Rush and the
OL,16,Flively Abdul Abdulmalik.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/3
