OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F391A1778483138
OL,3,CRochdale secures promotion with
OL,4,Cpenalty shootout win
OL,6,FDale, who were denied automatic
OL,7,Fpromotion in heartbreaking fashion on
OL,8,Fthe final day of the regular season,
OL,9,Fpulled one back in the 78th minute
OL,10,Fthrough Tyler Smith and Mani
OL,11,FDieseruvwe's header made it 2-2 deep
OL,12,Finto stoppage time.
OL,14,FNeither side could find a winner in
OL,15,Fextra time but Rochdale prevailed 3-1
OL,16,Fon penalties after goalkeeper Oliver
OL,17,FWhatmuff, on loan from Manchester
OL,18,FCity, saved from Callum Reynolds and
OL,19,FRush before Cameron Coxe hit the
OL,20,Fcrossbar.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/3
